  old

  03 Jan 2012; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  libbluray-0.2.1-r1.ebuild, libbluray-9999.ebuild:
  Remove USE="xine" and PDEPEND for libbluray-xine because the plug-in is now
  part of xine-lib since 1.2.0.

